Hacking dircproxy
-----------------

If you want to hack on dircproxy, it will make your life easier to have
the following packages installed:

	GNU autoconf 2.5x
	GNU automake 1.6.x


Hacker's configure options
--------------------------

'--enable-debug'
	Run on the foreground and output a log of debugging information
	about what dircproxy is doing.

'--enable-maintainer-mode'
	Causes the various autotool-generated files to be automatically
	regenerated if you modify their sources.


